{"tid":689702,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"我最近買左支新鏡頭","createTime":"2018-06-04T09:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T10:03:36.000Z","uid":104387,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5cde112a11aca6e9105bb20629001d95cca175","tid":689702,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"今日經過去觀塘廣場,順便去睇下有無uv 買. 近頂樓有一間賣攝影器材的. <br />\n<br />\n我問老闆有無uv 鏡. 佢令左一塊出來. 係我未見過的牌子. 因為我平日無研究開uv 鏡. 而香港來來去去都係果幾牌子. 所以我問佢幾錢. 佢開價150.我話我預算得120. 佢話130俾你啦.俾我地d 細舖賺下啦. <br />\n<br />\n我見價錢同我預計的差唔多. 就買左. 點知我朋友同我講係淘寶買,12蚊塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97b09fcd28fa54d071dd7d6d6a50a69e80b637c","tid":689702,"uid":163554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:29:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"749f7eb8b4a50a07c488ecc4d564aaa367656cb3","tid":689702,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:29:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72c256d2190917d4f3e3839d9f8a809fcb37dbbd","tid":689702,"uid":78620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"淘寶貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開名啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8299808e41849492bf08c4115688df2fbb4ffc4c","tid":689702,"uid":117044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:31:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c073500547e14753c50f2cdf9ebf23aef1cadcbb","tid":689702,"uid":104387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72c256d2190917d4f3e3839d9f8a809fcb37dbbd","tid":689702,"uid":78620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"淘寶貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <